channel.title: Comments on: A Corona SDK Developer Interview with iNSERT.CODE’s Adam Smith

item.title: By: Charles McKeever
item.dc:creator: Charles McKeever
item.description: I need to catch up with Adam and see what he is up to. I saw that he had done some tutorials on creating code that shuffle cards. Maybe I can get him on the Corona Geek show soon.
